{"tid":2033491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新風向 批鬥bno","createTime":"2020-05-24T16:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:17:28.000Z","uid":35534,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6511e82b1caa910d3d64c66b338ae7351a06afeb","tid":2033491,"uid":35534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:31:16.000Z","msg":"根本批唔批唔係我地話事， 批左先算， d 五毛係咩分化， 手足咪中計"},{"pid":"3c645ddbdd7aa5f89f652ce2c933579eceb94a0b","tid":2033491,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"連登=5毛集散地=狗監視場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6926c516a8befde7f98c43b680396ee297f2d2a2","tid":2033491,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:52:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"5eb73c2a1f6cc01aa1f1d7c05fce7a447e34468b","tid":2033491,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:54:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請</strong></span>。"},{"pid":"29fc0ccfa95a47b247ddedf1f0d2994949572b0b","tid":2033491,"uid":114901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T19:54:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e3b31528aa14f63b00121c1bbedc387806eef047","tid":2033491,"uid":56729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T20:04:18.000Z","msg":"五毛多過人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f97448b277feb9966e64181ed04375fe425c19b","tid":2033491,"uid":332602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T20:25:05.000Z","msg":"雙非手足點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e071739338ad689cd7a7479437fe62795997893c","tid":2033491,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n走嘅香港人留低嘅都係香港人打嘅係同一場戰爭<br />\n不分化"}]}